# Follow-Up: Prediction Strategies

Follow-up analyses test whether participants used the two F0/stress cues in the stimuli for online prediction. **Verb match** tests whether the verb's stress pattern was used to predict the suffix (mismatch = prediction error at suffix). **Noun match** tests whether the noun's F0 contour was used to predict the upcoming verb (mismatch = prediction error at verb). Each factor was tested in a separate model that included the other two factors (verb stress, the other match factor) as additive controls. The full 3-way interaction with group and phase was tested, along with its component 2-way interactions.

